'''Deportivo Teculután'''  is a [[Guatemala]]n [[football club]] based in [[Teculután]], [[Zacapa Department]].

They play their home games in the [[Estadio Julio Héctor Paz Castilla]].<ref>[http://www.worldstadiums.com/middle_america/countries/guatemala.shtml Stadiums of Guatemala] - World Stadiums</ref>

==History==
They have been playing in [[Primera División de Ascenso|Guatemala's second division]]<ref>[http://www.rsssf.com/tablesg/guat2010.html#2claugrupob Guatemala 2009/2010] - RSSSF</ref> since 2004, after they spent 3 seasons at the highest domestic level.<ref>[http://www.rsssf.com/tablesg/guat04.html Guatemala 2003/04] - RSSSF</ref>

