The '''Ghost of the B''' ({{lang-es|Fantasma de la B}}) is a joke mainly used by sports fans in Latin America to fans of rival club in danger of descending into "B" Division.<ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.ambito.com/noticia.asp?id=694941|title= Ahora, el "Fantasma de la B" llama a los hinchas del "Rojo"|trans-title=Now, the "Ghost of the B" calls the fans of the "Red"|language= Spanish|author= |date= June 28, 2013|work= |publisher= Ámbito Financiero|accessdate=July 29, 2013}}</ref><ref>[http://www.marca.com/2015/05/15/futbol/futbol_internacional/argentina/1431665808.html Los aficionados de Boca se mofan de River Plate con 'el fantasma de la B'] - [Marca]</ref><ref>[http://deportes.terra.com.ar/futbol/siguen-las-burlas-a-river-encontra-al-fantasma-de-la-b,d4ab30bb32eb0310VgnVCM4000009bf154d0RCRD.html Siguen las burlas a River: Encontrá al fantasma de la 'B']</ref><ref>[http://www.infiernorojo.com/independiente/2010/02/racing-dueno-de-estos-afiches/ Racing, dueño de estos afiches]</ref><ref>[http://www.futbolizados.com/68169/fotos-el-fantasma-de-la-b-se-el-aparecio-a-deportivo-quito-en-casa-blanca/ El “fantasma de la B” se el apareció a Deportivo Quito en Casa Blanca]</ref>

The popularity of the character led to the inclusion of the mascot in a TV spot of Claudio Lozano for the [[2013 elections in Argentina]], this time as a joke for the candidate [[Daniel Filmus]].<ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.lanacion.com.ar/1603304-terragno-irreconocible-presenta-un-ciclo-de-cocina-en-la-web|title= El fantasma de la B llegó a la campaña|trans-title=The ghost of the B arrived to the campaign|language= Spanish|author= |date= July 22, 2013|work= |publisher= La Nación|accessdate=July 29, 2013}}</ref>

